Package: vlad
Type: Package
Title: Variable Life Adjusted Display
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Philipp", "Wittenberg", email = "pwitten@hsu-hh.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Maintainer: Philipp Wittenberg <pwitten@hsu-hh.de>
URL: http://github.com/wittenberg/vlad
BugReports: http://github.com/wittenberg/vlad/issues
Description: Contains functions to set up risk-adjusted quality control charts in health care. For the variable life adjusted display (VLAD) and RA-CUSUM based on log-likelihood ratio statistic parameters such as the Average Run Length (ARL) or control limits can be computed.
